					</m:mrow>
				</m:mrow>
			</m:mrow>
		</m:mrow>
	</m:math></para>
    <para id="id12263124">Therefore, since the jω axis is in the region of convergence of X(s), we can evaluate X(s) on the jω axis to obtain the Fourier transform.</para>
    <para id="id12263182"><m:math>
